      "utterance": "Prometheus exporter到Mimir的箭头标M，OpenTelemetry Exporter到Tempo的箭头标T就行，简洁一些。另外检查下，EA1应该在Alloy subgraph外面，它是数据源。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Auto-instrumenter",
        "Alloy",
        "Mimir",
